{"id":98418,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/华尔街日报中文版：垃圾围堵三峡大坝-译图/","date":"2010-08-14T17:23:19Z","modified":"2010-08-14T17:39:10Z","title":"华尔街日报中文版：垃圾围堵三峡大坝 | 译图","content":"<blockquote><p>Shared by  2020<br />\n<br />\n与译文配套的译图，共7张</p></blockquote>\n<h2><a href=\"https://yyii.org/tu/296/\">华尔街日报中文版：垃圾围堵三峡大坝</a></h2>\n<div>\n\t\t\t\t<span>Posted by xiaomi2020 on 2010年08月4日 [<a href=\"https://yyii.org/wp-admin/post.php?action=edit&#038;post=296\" title=\"编辑文章\">Edit</a>]</span><br />\n\t\t\t\t<span><a href=\"https://yyii.org/tu/296/#respond\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Leave a comment ?\">Leave a comment</a></span><br />\n\t\t\t\t<span><a href=\"https://yyii.org/tu/296/#comments\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Go to comments ?\">Go to comments</a></span>\n\t\t\t</div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/01.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[296]\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"280\" /></a></div>\n<pre>原文链接：<a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100803/PHO163435.asp\">垃圾围堵三峡大坝</a>\n译者：华尔街日报中文版</pre>\n<p>说明：中国官方媒体周一报导称，长江流域大量的漂浮垃圾对三峡水电站的水闸造成威胁，垃圾可能阻塞大坝的航运闸门。与图片配套的译文<a title=\"垃圾围堵三峡打败\" href=\"https://www.google.com/buzz/113701623246327997042/BUoEKXH17vC/%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA-%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E6%88%90%E5%B1%B1-%E5%A8%81%E8%83%81%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%A1\">点击这里</a><br />\n<span></span></p>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/01.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[296]\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180px\" /></a></p>\n<div>maginechina/Zuma Press 《湖北日报》报导称，自7月雨季开始以来，三峡大坝前逐渐形成了厚达60厘米的漂浮层，约50,000平方米的水域被顺流而至的垃圾所覆盖。</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/02.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[296]\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180px\" /></a></p>\n<div>Xinhua/Zuma Press 《湖北日报》称，漂浮层的一些区域特别厚，人们甚至可以在上面行走。</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/03.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[296]\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/03.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180px\" /></a></p>\n<div>Imaginechina/Zuma Press 在湖北宜昌，一艘清漂船正在三峡大坝附近清理淤积在长江里的垃圾。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/04.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[296]\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/04.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180px\" /></a></p>\n<div>ChinaFotoPress/Zuma Press 《中国日报》报导称，尽管每天从三峡大坝打捞出近3,000顿的垃圾，但暴雨引发的洪水带来的垃圾增长过快，缺少足够的人力和设备对垃圾进行彻底的清理。</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/05.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[296]\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/05.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180px\" /></a></p>\n<div>Imaginechina/Zuma Press 有超过1.5亿人居住在三峡大坝上游，附近几个城市因为缺乏垃圾处理设施而将生活垃圾直接倾入江中。据《中国日报》报导，三峡集团每年为清除江面漂浮垃圾花费1,000万人民币。</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/06.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[296]\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/06.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180px\" /></a></p>\n<div>Xinhua/Zuma Press 三峡集团一位名叫陈雷的官员对《中国日报》说：“库区大量垃圾可能堵塞人字闸门（水闸的一种）。”</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/07.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[296]\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/TrashAccumulatesatThreeGorgesDam/07.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180px\" /></a></p>\n<div>Imagine China/Zuma Press 7月20日，三峡泄洪的壮观场面。中国认为这座花费220亿美元建造的大坝是个现代化奇迹。因为大坝自2008年落成后，水力发电解决了电荒，长江航运增加。但是批评人士指责这座世界上最大的大坝破坏了生态，而且使附近区域山体滑坡增加。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://beidaibiao.info\" target=\"_blank\">“要翻墙，用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[13770,20534],"tags":[13140,8800]}